  "texts": [
    "SeqLPD aims to tackle the place recognition problem by integrating deep learning-based point cloud description and a coarse-to-fine sequence matching strategy, resulting in notable improvements in loop closure detection.",
    "Despite the success of LPD-Net, it is still resource-intensive.",
    "In an effort to enhance performance while mitigating resource demands, Hui et al. (2022) proposed EPC-Net, an efficient point cloud learning network specifically designed for 3D-PCPR tasks.",
    "EPC-Net achieves commendable performance while effectively reducing memory requirement and inference time.",
    "Yin et al. (2018) proposed an end-to-end framework that utilizes low-dimensional feature matching instead of geometry matching for LiDAR-based long-term place recognition."
  ],
